{"word":"G5072 - τετράμηνον - tetrámēnon - tet-ram'-ay-non - Four months","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τετράμηνον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">tetrámēnon</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">tet-ram'-ay-non</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Four months</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"நாலுமாதம் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"of four months"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a compound of <a href=\"#/G5064 - τέσσαρες - téssares - tes'-sar-es/5064\">G5064</a> and <a href=\"#/G3376 - μήν - mḗn - mane/3376\">G3376</a>; a <i>four months'</i> space: - four months.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5062/5062\">G5062</a>, <a href=\"#/G5063/5063\">G5063</a>, <a href=\"#/G5064/5064\">G5064</a>, <a href=\"#/G5065/5065\">G5065</a>, <a href=\"#/G5066/5066\">G5066</a>, <a href=\"#/G5067/5067\">G5067</a>, <a href=\"#/G5068/5068\">G5068</a>, <a href=\"#/G5069/5069\">G5069</a>, <a href=\"#/G5070/5070\">G5070</a>, <a href=\"#/G5071/5071\">G5071</a>, <a href=\"#/G5072/5072\">G5072</a>, <a href=\"#/G5073/5073\">G5073</a>, <a href=\"#/G5074/5074\">G5074</a>, <a href=\"#/G5075/5075\">G5075</a>, <a href=\"#/G5076/5076\">G5076</a>"}]}